  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted, W-CON-01)",
  "description": "Synthetic adversarial package derived from the Morrison COU2 VAD hemolysis credibility assessment. The package records an Accepted decision despite the fact that the Model Form factor omits both requiredLevel and achievedLevel. The factor carries only a richly-written qualitative rationale, creating a factor-decision inconsistency (W-CON-01). All other twelve factors carry integer requiredLevel and achievedLevel values consistent with MRL 5 expectations.",
